c: 42
v: 22
t: "Iwe udzawaona anthu ochimwa ali ndi mantha chifukwa cha ntchito zawo ndipo ndithudi mazunzo adzadza pa iwo pamene iwo amene amakhulupirira ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, adzakhala ku Paradiso. Iwo adzalandira, kuchokera kwa Ambuye wawo zonse zimene adzafuna. Chimenechi ndicho chisomo chachikulu"